{
  "texts": [
    "A single image randomly selected from the posterior is displayed for THEMIS and Comrade.",
    "The THEMIS reconstruction of the GRMHD synthetic data uses a Hybrid Themage model.",
    "This figure clearly shows that a very wide range of morphology types can be recovered by all imaging pipelines.",
    "These simulations are based on the same (u, v) coverage of the 2018 EHT observation, and thus have a common point spread function (PSF).",
    "This ensures that the recovered structures by imaging pipelines are not artificially caused by the (u, v) coverage and/or the PSF, but rather come from the real structure imprinted in the data."
  ]
}